name: Spiritum Portals - Old Roads
description: As a spring broke forth in the year 2021 a final wisp of winter overcast cast a matte shadow upon the last trickles of melting snow, the mellow greens of sagebrush, the deep purple cacti, the iron red sands, soft pink quartz, and a dull blue sky. Fear of the plague lies heavy on the land and hope struggles to crawl forth.
